article.description: — Jordan Walker registered 18 points as UAB edged past Saint Louis 77-72 on Saturday.
article.headline: Walker scores 18 to lift UAB past Saint Louis 77-72
article.linkText: Walker scores 18 to lift UAB past Saint Louis 77-72
article.story: ST. LOUIS -- — Jordan Walker registered 18 points as UAB edged past Saint Louis 77-72 on Saturday. Michael Ertel had 16 points for UAB (7-2). KJ Buffen added 12 points. DeAndre Jones had 17 points for the Billikens (7-2), whose four-game win streak came to an end. Fred Thatch Jr. added 12 points. Francis Okoro had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
